    {
      "text": "Jackie Chan Adventures is a 2004 action video game based on the animated series of the same name, which focuses on a fictionalized version of Hong Kong action film star Jackie Chan. The game was developed by Atomic Planet Entertainment, published by Sony Pictures Television's sister company, Sony Computer Entertainment, and released for the PlayStation 2 on October 1, 2004, in Europe.\nThe game is compatible with the EyeToy. An Xbox version was also announced but ultimately never released.. Jackie, Jade, Uncle, Valmont and Shendu were voiced by their original actors.",
